                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>This meeting is listed in the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref
                        target="#pg_461">p. 461</ref>, but no record of the conversation has been
                    found. The visit of the Soviet Chargé d’Affaires lasted at most twenty minutes
                    and was presumably in the nature of a courtesy call.</p>
            </div>
